---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="How to support Controllo">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-base-200 text-white">
    <NavBar />
    <main class="max-w-3xl m-auto">
      <div class="hero mt-5">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to support Controllo</h1>
            <p class="pt-6 text-lg text-left">
              First of all we thank you for your interest in wanting to support
              Controllo.
            </p>
            <p class="pt-6 text-lg text-left">
              This project is free and open source. It is our desire to keep it
              that way and also make it viable and for that we need your help.
            </p>
            <p class="pt-6 text-lg text-left">You can support Controllo by:</p>
            <ul class="pt-6 text-lg text-left space-y-2">
              <li>
                ‚≠ê Leaving a star on the <a
                  href="https://github.com/dlcastillop/controllo"
                  class="link"
                  target="_blank">GitHub repo</a
                >.
              </li>
              <li>
                üëç Rating the extension on the <a
                  href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/controllo/bodddijlpmhpjplaajoigmejoglnjhif"
                  class="link"
                  target="_blank">Chrome Web Store</a
                >,
                <a
                  href="https://addons.mozilla.org/es/firefox/addon/controllo/"
                  class="link"
                  target="_blank">Firefox Browser Add-Ons</a
                >
                and <a
                  href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/controllo/hepodmbgelammobllblgaindjhahghgj"
                  class="link"
                  target="_blank">Edge Plugins</a
                >.
              </li>
              <li>ü§ù Sharing the extension with others.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="pt-6 text-lg text-left">Thank you!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
